data.description: Exceptional Opportunity! Meticulously maintained gem awaits its new owner! This like new 2 story, just over 2 years old, over 2600SF boasts top-notch craftsmanship & luxurious features. Nestled on a cul-de-sac in an established neighborhood with lush mature trees, sitings on a generous half-acre lot & backs to a scenic trail. Convenience is key - enjoy a short walk Waukees new Waterford Elementary (2024), Waterford & Barrett Boesen & Coyote Ridge Parks. This home is truly turn-key, sparing you the hassle. Outfitted w/a suite of high-end appliances: GE Profile fridge, gas range, 2nd oven, Maytag washer & dryer plus an array of added extras: Anderson storm door, August keyless entry, ADT security equipment, Levolor cordless blinds, fireplace tv mount, humidifier, fenced yard, & irrigation system. Step into your outdoor oasis: paver patio w/ tasteful landscaping. Rest easy with an egress window grate already in place. Don't miss a rare opportunity with motivated sellers relocation creates a perfect chance to call this beauty your home!
